# boom — pick the torch, light the gasoline fuse, watch the flame race into the
# TNT cluster and detonate (chipping the building behind it).
# frames 260  fps 30  scale 2  crf 24
move  6 218 28
click 14 218 28      # click the TORCH button (switches to BUILD)
move  22 120 180
click 30 120 180     # torch the LEFT end of the fuse
move  44 150 9       # park the cursor in the header (hides the probe label) and watch
